{"article_id":"09cBsfYmwnBBucXC","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Searchers `` currently suspect ''","depth":9},{"id":1,"text":"that the AirAsia jetliner","depth":11},{"id":2,"text":"that disappeared Sunday morning over the Java Sea","depth":11},{"id":3,"text":"is on the bottom of the ocean ,","depth":10},{"id":4,"text":"the head of the lead agency in the operation said today .","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"`` We currently suspect","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"that plane is located on the ocean floor , ''","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"Bambang Soelistyo , the head of Indonesia 's National Search and Rescue Agency said .","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"If the plane is found on the ocean floor ,","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"there would be a challenge","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"in getting the plane to the surface","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"because they do not have the `` submersible '' equipment ,","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"Soelistyo said .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"The plane 's Emergency Locator Transmitter should function automatically","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"and send warning signals ,","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"but no signal has been detected by control centers in Indonesia or in neighboring countries ,","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"Soelistyo said .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"Soelistyo confirmed","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"that Indonesia 's National Search and Rescue Agency is spearheading the search effort .","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"The AirAsia jet lost contact with air traffic control over the Java Sea during a flight to Singapore Sunday morning ,","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"shortly after the pilots requested a change of flight plan","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"because of weather .","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"The Australian Defence Force deployed a Royal Australian Air Force AP-3C Orion Maritime Patrol Aircraft","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"to assist in the search ,","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"the Australian Department of Defense announced .","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"The Orion took off from Darwin Monday morning local time","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"to join the search operations .","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"Ships","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"engaged in the search and rescue effort","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"reached the area","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"where the plane was believed to be lost around Belitung Island at approximately 6:49 a.m. ,","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"a spokeswoman for the Indonesian National Search and Rescue Agency said .","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"`` Current weather conditions are not desirable , ''","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"spokeswoman Annisa Noviantri said .","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"Darkness and bad weather had forced the suspension of the search about 5:30 p.m. local time Sunday evening ,","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"said Indonesian transport officials .","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"Flight QZ8501 , an Airbus A320-200 , lost contact with air traffic control in Jakarta at 6:17 a.m. Sunday local time near Belitung Island , Indonesia ,","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"after the flight left Surabaya ,","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"Indonesian Air Transport Director Djoko Murjatmodjo said during a news conference Sunday .","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"The flight ,","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"which had at least 161 people on board ,","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"was scheduled to land in Singapore at 7:57 a.m. local time .","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"`` We are deeply shocked and saddened by this incident , ''","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"said Sunu Widyatmoko , CEO of AirAsia Indonesia .","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"`` We are cooperating with the relevant authorities to the fullest extent","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"to determine the cause of this incident .","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"In the meantime , our main priority is keeping the families of our passengers and colleagues informed on the latest developments . ''","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"Widyatmoko said","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"the airline had mobilized a support team","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"to help families of the passengers .","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"The flight was piloted by Captain Iriyanto ,","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"who had a total of 20,537 flying hours ,","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"according to a statement from AirAsia .","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"More than 6,000 of Iriyanto 's flying hours were on an Airbus A320 .","depth":5},{"id":54,"text":"The first officer , Remi Emmanuel Plesel , had 2,275 flying hours with AirAsia Indonesia ,","depth":5},{"id":55,"text":"according to the airline .","depth":5},{"id":56,"text":"consultant Col. Stephen Ganyard said","depth":5},{"id":57,"text":"weather may have played a role in whatever happened to the plane","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"but several questions remained .","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"`` We 're looking for clues","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"and at this point there are very few clues , ''","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"he said .","depth":5},{"id":62,"text":"The six-year-old aircraft was on its submitted flight plan","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"but the pilot requested a deviation","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"because of en-route weather","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"before communication with the aircraft was lost ,","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"AirAsia said .","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"Murjatmodjo said","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"the pilot also requested to increase altitude to 38,000 feet from 32,000 feet","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"to `` avoid clouds . ''","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"Thunderstorms were reported in the area with clouds up to 50,000 feet .","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"While ground control in Jakarta approved the pilot 's request","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"to divert the flight ,","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"the request","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"to raise elevation","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"had n't been approved","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"before losing contact with the plane ,","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"said Murjatmodjo .","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"The plane had been in the air for about 41 minutes","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"when contact was lost .","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"I am touched by the massive show of support especially from my fellow airlines .","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"This is my worse nightmare .","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"But there is no stopping .","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"- Tony Fernandes","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"( @ tonyfernandes )","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"December 28 , 2014","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"The jet was flying at the regular cruising altitude for most jetliners","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"- 32,000 feet -","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"when the signal was lost ,","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"according to flight tracking website Flightradar24 .","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"No distress reports came from the plane ,","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"officials said .","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"The aircraft had undergone its last scheduled maintenance on November 16 , 2014 .","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"The flight manifest for the jet showed","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"there were 155 passengers on board plus seven crew members ,","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"although the Indonesian transport ministry only reported six crew members .","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"Of the passengers , 149 were Indonesians ,","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"three were South Korean ,","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"and there was one traveler each from Malaysia , Singapore and the United Kingdom ,","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"according to AirAsia .","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"AirAsia said","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"the crew members consisted of six Indonesians and one person from France .","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"The Civil Aviation Authority of Singapore said","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"it was informed about the missing plane by Jakarta ground control about half an hour after contact was lost .","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"The Singapore air force and the navy were activated with two C-130","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"ready to assist Indonesia authorities in the search ,","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"according to the aviation authority .","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"`` We remain ready to provide any assistance","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"to support the search and rescue effort , ''","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"the CAAS said .","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"Saddened to hear of missing flight # QZ8501 .","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"My thoughts are with the passengers and their families .","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"- LHL","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"- Lee Hsien Loong","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"( @ leehsienloong )","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"December 28 , 2014","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"A waiting area was set up at Changi Airport in Singapore ,","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"where the plane had been scheduled to land ,","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"with facilities and support for relatives and friends of the passengers on the plane .","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"At Juanda International Airport in Surabaya , dozens of relatives sat in a room ,","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"many of them talking on mobile phones","depth":13},{"id":121,"text":"and crying .","depth":13},{"id":122,"text":"Some looked dazed ,","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"the Associated Press reported .","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"The White House said","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"President Obama was briefed on the flight .","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"A State Department spokesperson said","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"the U.S. is `` ready to assist in any way","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"that 's helpful . ''","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"This is the third air incident this year for Malaysian-based airlines .","depth":7},{"id":130,"text":"In July , another Malaysia Airlines jet was shot down over Ukraine ,","depth":8},{"id":131,"text":"killing all 298 on board .","depth":8},{"id":132,"text":"Very sad to hear","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"that AirAsia Indonesia QZ8501 is missing .","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"My thoughts are with the families .","depth":8},{"id":135,"text":"Malaysia stands ready to help .","depth":7},{"id":136,"text":"- Mohd Najib Tun Razak","depth":8},{"id":137,"text":"( @ NajibRazak )","depth":8},{"id":138,"text":"December 28 , 2014","depth":7},{"id":139,"text":"In March , Malaysia Airlines flight 370 , a wide-bodied Boeing 777 with 239 people on board , lost contact with air traffic control","depth":9},{"id":140,"text":"soon after taking off from Kuala Lumpur for Beijing .","depth":9},{"id":141,"text":"It has n't been found .","depth":8},{"id":142,"text":"`` It 's really disheartening , ''","depth":9},{"id":143,"text":"said Ganyard .","depth":9},{"id":144,"text":"`` It just should n't happen in this day and age . ''","depth":8},{"id":145,"text":"Get real-time updates","depth":3},{"id":146,"text":"as this story unfolds .","depth":3},{"id":147,"text":"To start ,","depth":5},{"id":148,"text":"just `` star '' this story in ' phone app .","depth":5},{"id":149,"text":"Download for iPhone here or for Android here .","depth":4},{"id":150,"text":"To be notified about our live weekend digital reports ,","depth":5},{"id":151,"text":"tap here .","depth":5},{"id":152,"text":"With reporting by ' Ben Gittelson and Gillian Mohney .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":305,"left":297,"right":304,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":297,"left":208,"right":296,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":208,"left":202,"right":207,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":202,"left":171,"right":201,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":171,"left":169,"right":170,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":169,"left":160,"right":168,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":160,"left":157,"right":159,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"